---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">

  <main class="py-8">
    <Hero 
      title="Privacy Policy" 
      description="Your privacy matters. Here's how we handle your data across Impact Orbit Creative Group and its brands."
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-secondary-500">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-4xl mx-auto">

          <p class="mb-8 text-white dark:text-white">
            <strong>Effective Date:</strong> 1 February 2026
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            <strong>Impact Orbit Creative Group Ltd</strong> (“we”, “our”, or “us”) is a private limited company registered in England and Wales (Company No. 15207389).
          </p>
          <p class="mb-6">
            Our registered office is:
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic mb-8">
            DOCK – Space City<br />
            75 Exploration Drive<br />
            Leicester, LE4 5NU<br />
            United Kingdom
          </address>
          <p class="mb-6">
            We act as a data controller under the UK General Data Protection Regulation (UK GDPR) and are registered with the Information Commissioner’s Office (ICO), Registration Number: <strong>ZB640949</strong>.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-8">
            <strong>Green Orbit Space Communications & PR</strong> is a strategic communications and public relations brand operating within Impact Orbit Creative Group, focused on the global space sector.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">2. What Personal Data We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We may collect personal data when you interact with our websites, brands, or services.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mt-6 mb-2">Website and Brand Interactions</h3>
          <ul class="mb-6 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>IP address and referring domain.</li>
            <li>Device information such as operating system, browser type, and screen resolution.</li>
            <li>Location, language preferences, pages visited, and session duration.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="mt-6 mb-2">Service and Communication Interactions</h3>
          <ul class="mb-6 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Information you provide when contacting us or using our services.</li>
            <li>Communication preferences and consent choices.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="mt-6 mb-2">Analytics and Tracking</h3>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We use analytics services to understand engagement and improve user experience. These services collect pseudonymised usage data and do not sell personal information.
          </p>
          <ul class="mb-6 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>
              <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-500 hover:underline">
                Google Analytics Privacy Policy
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://www.gosquared.com/legal/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-500 hover:underline">
                GoSquared Privacy Policy
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="mt-6 mb-2">Cookies</h3>
          <p class="mb-8">
            We use cookies to enhance functionality, analyse performance, and remember preferences. For full details, see our
            <a href="/cookie-policy" class="text-accent-500 hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a>.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="mb-8 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>To deliver and improve our services and platforms.</li>
            <li>To send communications and updates in line with your preferences.</li>
            <li>To personalise content, campaigns, and outreach.</li>
            <li>To analyse website performance and engagement.</li>
            <li>To respond to enquiries and support requests.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-8">
            We do not sell your personal data.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">4. Who We Share Your Data With</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We may share limited personal data with trusted third parties that support analytics and service delivery:
          </p>
          <ul class="mb-8 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Google Analytics</li>
            <li>GoSquared Analytics</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-8">
            All partners process data under GDPR-compliant agreements and their own privacy policies. We do not share data for unrelated third-party marketing without explicit consent.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="mb-8">
            Personal data is retained only for as long as necessary for the purposes outlined in this policy. When no longer required, data is securely deleted or anonymised. Backup data is securely isolated until deletion is possible.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">6. Data Security</h2>
          <ul class="mb-8 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Encryption of data at rest and in transit.</li>
            <li>Role-based access controls and strong password policies.</li>
            <li>Regular staff training on security and privacy.</li>
            <li>Automated vulnerability scanning and static code analysis.</li>
            <li>API key rotation and optional mutual TLS (mTLS).</li>
            <li>Privacy by design and data minimisation practices.</li>
            <li>Background checks for staff handling sensitive data.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">7. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            If you are located in the UK, EEA, or Switzerland, you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="mb-8 list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
            <li>Access your personal data.</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion.</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing.</li>
            <li>Request data portability.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">8. Do-Not-Track Signals</h2>
          <p class="mb-8">
            We do not currently respond to browser “Do-Not-Track” signals, as no universal standard exists. This policy may be updated if standards change.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">9. Policy Updates</h2>
          <p class="mb-8">
            We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect legal or operational changes. Significant updates will be communicated where reasonably possible.
          </p>

          <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">
            For questions or requests relating to personal data:
          </p>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-6">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>

          <address class="not-italic text-sm mb-8">
            Impact Orbit Creative Group – Green Orbit Space Communications & PR<br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:hello@greenorbit.space" class="text-accent-500 hover:underline">hello@greenorbit.space</a><br />
            Phone: +44 116 483 0155
          </address>

          <p class="text-sm mb-2">
            You may also contact the UK Information Commissioner’s Office:
          </p>

          <address class="not-italic text-sm">
            Wycliffe House, Water Lane<br />
            Wilmslow, Cheshire, SK9 5AF<br />
            Phone: 0303 123 1113<br />
            <a href="https://www.ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent-500 hover:underline">
              www.ico.org.uk
            </a>
          </address>

        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Full-Width CTA -->
  <section class="w-full bg-secondary-500 py-16 text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to collaborate?</h2>
      <p class="mb-8 text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-200">
        Let’s drive responsible growth for your organisation. Get in touch for a custom package or exploratory call.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-block w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-accent-500 hover:bg-accent-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition text-lg sm:text-xl"
      >
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>